fields.value: Theoretical studies involving two Diels-Alder reactions under solvent-free conditions

dsDescriptionValue.value: Transition states of two Diels-Alder reactions are investigated using various theoretical methods including DFT. 1. Reaction between 1-methoxybutadiene and acrolein. 2. Reaction between thiophene and maleic anhydride.
